        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Aurelio Basileio <lb n="2"/>viro ducenario <expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>rationis castrensis <lb n="4"/>ordo decurionum ob <lb n="5"/>tanto amore quam erga <lb n="6"/>patriam nostram praes<lb break="no" n="7"/>tare consuevit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Corona mit dorischen Fries, patera, urceus und vegetabilen Motiven. (B): D&amp;apos;Avino: Z. 3/4: Zeilenfall fehlt.</p>
            </div>
